Koryūsai - Hinazuru of the Chōjiya, Kamuro Yasoji and Yasono, Shinzō Orizuru, Kiyotsuru, and Sayotsuru.jpg|''Hinazuru of the Chōjiya''<br />[[Koryūsai]], {{circa|1778–80}}
